        </h2>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-[#888] font-geist leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto">
          Histórias reais de mulheres que decidiram parar, olhar pra dentro e se reencontrar.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Carrossel de Depoimentos -->
      <div class="relative reveal delay-1 mb-16">
        <!-- Scroll container -->
        <div id="testimonialSlider" class="flex gap-5 overflow-x-auto no-scrollbar scroll-smooth snap-x snap-mandatory px-6 md:px-12 py-4">

          <!-- Card 1 -->
          <div class="testimonial-card w-[85vw] md:w-[400px] shrink-0 snap-center glass-panel rounded-2xl p-8 relative group hover:border-[#444] transition-all duration-500">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-2xl bg-[url('https://grainy-gradients.vercel.app/noise.svg')] opacity-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
            <div class="absolute top-6 right-6"><i data-lucide="quote" class="w-8 h-8 text-white/[0.06]"></i></div>
            <div class="flex gap-1 mb-5 relative z-10">
              <i data-lucide="star" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400 fill-amber-400"></i>
              <i data-lucide="star" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400 fill-amber-400"></i>
              <i data-lucide="star" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400 fill-amber-400"></i>
              <i data-lucide="star" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400 fill-amber-400"></i>
              <i data-lucide="star" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400 fill-amber-400"></i>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[15px] text-[#888] font-geist leading-relaxed italic mb-8 relative z-10">"Eu achei que estava apenas cansada da minha rotina, mas a verdade é que eu estava exausta de tentar dar conta de tudo e me deixar para depois. A imersão com a Fabianna foi um divisor de águas. Eu finalmente saí do piloto automático e resgatei a mulher potente que eu sou."</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 relative z-10">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/[0.08] flex items-center justify-center"><span class="font-jakarta font-medium text-white text-sm">C</span></div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-sm font-jakarta font-medium text-white">Camila R.</div>
                <div class="text-xs font-geist text-orange-400">Empresária</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 2 — Featured (rotating border) -->
          <div class="testimonial-card w-[85vw] md:w-[400px] shrink-0 snap-center relative rounded-2xl p-[1px] overflow-hidden shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(147,51,234,0.08)] transition-all duration-500">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#1a1a1a]"></div>
