          <!-- Card 1 -->
          <div class="wall-card w-[85vw] md:w-[400px] shrink-0 snap-center glass-panel rounded-2xl p-8 relative group hover:border-[#444] transition-all duration-500">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-2xl bg-[url('https://grainy-gradients.vercel.app/noise.svg')] opacity-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
            <div class="absolute top-6 right-6"><i data-lucide="quote" class="w-8 h-8 text-white/[0.06]"></i></div>
            <div class="flex gap-1 mb-5 relative z-10">
              <i data-lucide="star" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400 fill-amber-400"></i><i data-lucide="star" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400 fill-amber-400"></i><i data-lucide="star" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400 fill-amber-400"></i><i data-lucide="star" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400 fill-amber-400"></i><i data-lucide="star" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400 fill-amber-400"></i>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[15px] text-[#888] font-geist leading-relaxed italic mb-8 relative z-10">"Sempre tive medo de me expor em grupo, mas o ambiente que a Fabi cria é de tanto respeito que me senti em casa nos primeiros 5 minutos. Ver outras mulheres lidando com os mesmos bloqueios que eu tirou um peso enorme das minhas costas."</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 relative z-10">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/[0.08] flex items-center justify-center"><span class="font-jakarta font-medium text-white text-sm">J</span></div>
              <div><div class="text-sm font-jakarta font-medium text-white">Juliana P.</div><div class="text-xs font-geist text-orange-400">Empreendedora</div></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 2 — Featured (DS: gradientes internos, sem rotate border) -->
          <div class="wall-card w-[85vw] md:w-[400px] shrink-0 snap-center relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(147,51,234,0.08)] border border-purple-500/20 transition-all duration-500" style="background-color: #0a0a0a; background-image: radial-gradient(at 0% 0%, rgba(147,51,234,0.12) 0px, transparent 65%), radial-gradient(at 100% 100%, rgba(217,70,239,0.12) 0px, transparent 65%); box-shadow: 0px -16px 24px 0px rgba(255,255,255,0.05) inset">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-2xl bg-[url('https://grainy-gradients.vercel.app/noise.svg')] opacity-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
            <div class="absolute top-6 right-6"><i data-lucide="quote" class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-400/10"></i></div>
            <div class="p-8 relative z-10">
              <div class="flex gap-1 mb-5">
                <i data-lucide="star" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400 fill-amber-400"></i><i data-lucide="star" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400 fill-amber-400"></i><i data-lucide="star" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400 fill-amber-400"></i><i data-lucide="star" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400 fill-amber-400"></i><i data-lucide="star" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400 fill-amber-400"></i>
              </div>
              <p class="text-[15px] text-[#888] font-geist leading-relaxed italic mb-8">"A energia daquele lugar é indescritível. A gente chora, ri, se abraça... Saí de lá com uma rede de apoio maravilhosa e uma clareza absurda dos meus próximos passos."</p>
